Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:54.96,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}今亦得见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:01:00.53,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}逆风疾走 赶上电车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:03.52,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蕙芷芬芳 色状霓虹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:06.72,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向阳步道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:11.81,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}鹿撞愈疾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:18.94,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}散学廊下 钟声回响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:22.34,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}无奇世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:26.75,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}渐始闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:33.47,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}走而出者 慕君之思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:39.48,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}眼底心内 如系如缚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:45.30,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}心潮难平 盈溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:51.43,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}重之以君意 可与我知否
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.35,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}此心君可解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:57.26,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}此意望君知
